-- Egypt Telecom Regulator to Meet on New License Plan, Borsa Says
-- B y   A h m e d   A .   N a m a t a l l a
-- 2012-08-05T09:31:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-05/egypt-telecom-regulator-to-meet-on-new-license-plan-borsa-says.html
Egypt ’s  National Telecommunication
Regulatory Authority  will hold a board meeting to finalize its
plan to offer a mobile virtual network operator license,  Al
Borsa  newspaper reported, citing Executive President Amr Badawi.  The board will meet to determine rules for pricing and
timing of the license, which would allow its holder to offer
mobile phone services using an existing operator’s network,  the
Cairo-based daily said. The paper did not say when the meeting
would be held.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ahmed A. Namatalla in Cairo at 
 anamatalla@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
